OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather wet start with a band
OL,6,Fof rain breaking up into a mix of
OL,7,Fbright spells and showers. Some of the
OL,8,Fshowers will be heavy, but northern
OL,9,Fareas tending to turn drier for a time
OL,10,Fthroughout the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late spells of sunshine
OL,13,Fin the east this evening. Otherwise
OL,14,Frain will spread across Wales
OL,15,Fovernight, accompanied by blustery
OL,16,Fwinds. A milder night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
